  "verdict": "PARTIALLY SUPPORTED: a positive TF organisation appears in some marine-West components but not all/clean of the East contrast. Marine sectors with positive Ro-TF slope (CI>0): Bellingshausen+WAIS-Pacific; with positive thinning-TF slope: none; East Antarctica Ro-TF flat/negative. TF = Schmidtko-2014 shelf-bottom CT - CT_freezing(SA,p) (TEOS-10).",
